    <svcsubproc>
        <title>Optional Driver Storage Compartment</title>
        <para>The driver storage compartment is located above the windshield in the step well area (optional). The
            compartment has a removable hinged door.
        </para>
        <figure id="f4700554" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g4700554.webp" filename="../figg47/g4700554.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="272px"
                     scalefitheight="272px"/>
            <caption>Figure 54. Optional Overhead Storage Compartment</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">FRONT BULKHEAD</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">STORAGE COMPARTMENT WITH HINGED COVER</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">FIRST AID KIT AND MOUNTING</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">DRIVER INTERIOR REAR VIEW MIRROR</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <para>
            <title>Glove Box Storage Compartment</title>
        </para>
        <para>The glove box storage compartment on the RE school bus is located outboard of the main bus heater in the
            step well area. The glove box assembly is a removable component of the step well entry.
        </para>
        <figure id="f4700555" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g4700555" filename="../figg47/g4700555.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="272px"
                     scalefitheight="272px"/>
            <caption>Figure 55. Glove Box Assembly</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">GLOVE BOX ASSEMBLY</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">AIR VENTS</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
